        # Get API Key
        
        1 - Go to [DeepAI](https://deepai.org) and create an account
        
        2 - Verify by clicking on the URL sent by DeepAI to your E-Mail
        
        3 - Go to [DeepAI Dashboard](https://deepai.org/dashboard) and get your API Key
        
        
